<!--
    The homepage partial for the website.
    This partial is used for the homepage.
    Features of this partial:
        - Search for pets. Should have four input boxes: city, state, zip, and pet-type. Should be a dropdown menu for the state.
        - Link to signup/Login pages.
        - Logo of the website "public/assets/www/media/logo.png"
